            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "So i am actually studying my 10th std in this school right now.. it has some drawbacks as well as some plus points..\n\n*THE DRAWBACKS*:A complete jail ,Only they are best in education .. No extra curricular activities ,no tour, ,no programs,no canteen,no annual day, no childrens day, no teachers day or celebrations.\n\n*THE PLUS POINTS*: The school has a very pleasant environment and a lot of trees gives a greenish atmosphere.. The restrooms are most of the time clean..The Staffs are kind and caring, The teachers are best at their work and they help their students at all cost..\n\n*THE CONCLUSION*: Students can come here and  get the best education and also social speaking skills  mainly they will learn and speak English very fluently, but their is no hope for sports and other activities .\n\n*THANK YOU*",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
